Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:20.93,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}爛れた世界だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:25.63,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}嘆いてるその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.51,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}神風よ誘え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.05,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}未知なる方ヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.05,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}沸き上がる情熱と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:42.25,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燻る魂が胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:46.71,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:49.23,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.62,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:59.08,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鋼の牙を起て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:07.65,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと声を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:14.86,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}たった―つのこの身焦がして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.73,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}血が枯れはてるまで進む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:32.13,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}遠い空から反る光もこの身に当たり消え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.67,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}散ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:42.35,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}荒ぶる波動を内に抱えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:56.25,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}握り締めた手の疼きは誰も知るはずなく！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.06,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊せ Break & Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:02.58,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}音も無く迫る闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.98,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光を灯す為 今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.30,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊すFate & Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.91,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生まれ持った衝動で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:20.30,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを掴み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.04,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:01:01.28,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下击断烦恼的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:05.68,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫无用处的自尊在垃圾回收日舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:10.68,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}猎取一切的武士疯狂起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:14.41,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.77,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:20.93,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:25.63,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在叹息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.51,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟随神风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.05,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向着未知之处前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.05,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的热情与
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:42.25,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}熏染的灵魂勒紧胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:46.71,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃烧的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:49.23,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.62,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:59.08,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:07.65,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:14.86,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}继续这不羁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦这唯一的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.73,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}前进直到血干枯之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:32.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}远方天空反射过来的光照耀此身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.67,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}消逝散落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:42.35,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}胸中充满激烈的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:56.25,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}紧握的手的疼痛谁人能知!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:59.06,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:02.58,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悄无声息迫近的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.98,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}只为点亮光明  现在正是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.30,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:13.91,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}用与生俱来的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:20.30,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}抓住一切 就是现在 只要……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.04,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}将真实握在手中！
